-- Fannie, Freddie shares plummet on NYSE after market open
-- 
-- Fri Jul 11, 2008 9:44am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/07/11/us-fanniemae-freddiemac-stocks-idUSN11186120080711

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Fannie Mae FRE.N and Freddie Mac FRE.N plunged after the market open on Friday, after a New York Times report said the U.S. government is considering a takeover of the housing finance giants amid funding problems. 

 Freddie Mac shares fell 49 percent to $4.07, while Fannie Mae dropped 46.2 percent to $7.10 on the New York Stock Exchange. (Reporting by  Kristina Cooke ; Editing by Theodore d'Afflisio)